<p><img src="http://www.jack003.com/static/img/blog/python_challenge12/2.gif" alt="2" /></p>

<p><img src="http://www.jack003.com/static/img/blog/python_challenge12/3.png" alt="3" /></p>

<p><img src="http://www.jack003.com/static/img/blog/python_challenge12/4.jpg" alt="4" /></p>

<p>最后一张图片的字母划掉了，所以答案是：<strong>disproportional</strong></p>
